# Title: MSI Installation From Web
# Author: Stamatis Chatzimangou
# Date: 2022-10-23
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects installation of a remote msi file from web.
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1218, attack.t1218.007
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/application/msiinstaller/win_msi_install_from_web.yml

Data="*://*" EventID IN (1040, 1042) Provider_Name="MsiInstaller"